From: Daniel Burrows <dburrows@debian.org>
Date: Sun, 20 Jun 2010 14:53:38 -0700
Subject: Uniformly use $(srcdir) when grabbing files for install using $(wildcard), so wildcarded files get picked up even if the build directory isn't the source directory. Most importantly, this means that translated defaults are available again. (Closes: #586508, #586511)

